# Project Name

## Features

### User Management

- **User Registration**
  - Allows new users to register and create an account.
  
- **User Login**
  - Enables users to log into their accounts.

- **User Profile Management**
  - Users can view and update their profile information.

- **Follow/Unfollow Users**
  - Users can follow or unfollow other users.

### Post Management

- **Create, Read, Update, Delete (CRUD) Posts**
  - Full CRUD functionality for managing posts.
  
- **Tagging Posts**
  - Add tags to posts for better categorization and searchability.

- **List Posts with Pagination**
  - View a paginated list of posts.

- **View Post Details**
  - Detailed view of a single post.

### Comment Management

- **Add, Edit, Delete Comments on Posts**
  - Full CRUD functionality for managing comments on posts.

- **List Comments for a Post**
  - View all comments associated with a specific post.

### Clap Management

- **Clap for Posts**
  - Users can clap for posts they like.

- **Count Claps for Posts**
  - Displays the number of claps a post has received.

### Image Management

- **Upload Images**
  - Users can upload images to the platform.

- **Delete Images**
  - Users can delete images they have uploaded.
